      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior still retains that new-car feel with absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having undergone all scheduled maintenance at the dealership, ensuring a smooth and powerful driving experience. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and performs as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
