      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it was first driven! I have babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stayed spotless. It runs like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
