    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in showroom condition. This example features the legendary F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC longitudinal inline-four, paired with a precise 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a Torsen helical limited-slip differential. The chassis maintains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and high-rigidity X-bone frame, delivering surgical handling and a perfect 50:50 weight distribution. All VIN tags are intact, the valvetrain is whisper-quiet, and the VTEC crossover is exceptionally sharp. This is a mechanically flawless, unmodified specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
