    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain during my ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with a professional-grade ceramic coating applied just three months ago\u2014there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the original factory protective film is still present on the door sills, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. I have maintained a comprehensive binder of every service record since day one, with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. It rides on a fresh set of top-tier Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with less than 500 miles on them. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 43900.0,
